      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used in the simulation must be verified under a documented quality management system with version control and regression testing.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical R19.2 was used under an ISO 9001-certified QMS. Version control logs and regression test reports were reviewed and found compliant with the required level."
    },
    {
