      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantities of interest (construct stiffness, yield load) must be directly linked to the regulatory submission metric.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness and yield load are the primary endpoints specified in ASTM F1717 and referenced in the 510(k) predicate comparison. Direct linkage to submission metric is established."
    },
