    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged and accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol scope. Overall model risk level 3 is adequately addressed by the ensemble approach and multi-laboratory validation dataset.",
